 "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 11:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872861703,45974302,8102]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60364819]黄金林檎[/uid] (2026-06-25 11:12):[/b]<br/><br/>这里感觉有点看不懂<br/>按照狼大的预测 这轮3-5行情最后会在4K3左右结束<br/>目前是4107站稳的第四天 离4K3还有差不多200点的距离<br/>但是今天看起来科技里的机构出货迹象比较明显 包括狼大也减仓了铁盒<br/>疑惑就是现在资金切了新能源后真的能承接芯的作用一起把指数带上去吗 不可能真的去拉白水吧<br/>目前光也有点蛆 存储倒是看起来承接很强 但总体都有点摇摇欲坠的感觉<br/>4107站稳后的技术派承接资金似乎没有想象中多<br/>不懂狼图的进度发展到了哪个阶段 个人感觉像是9<br/>难道说毕业照可能到不了4K3了？[s:ac:愁[/quote]<br/>早盘已经放量3000E在你嘴巴里面是不算多？下午继续补量呢<br/>现在是跷跷板  光在压指数<br/>万一最后不压指数呢？<br/>金融+半导体+光+新能源同时上去  2天不就干到位置了？你不看看现在两融多少吗？你知道带杠杆在里面的多少吗", "lou": 3442, "content_length": 198, "reply_to": 872861703, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782357496}, {"pid": 872863167, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 174, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 11:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "机构不是拉升的时候卖 什么时候卖？跌停时候卖吗？你以为是你们这些散户？<br/>你们到底知不知道现在半导体+光的日成交量占比大盘成交的多少？", "lou": 3443, "content_length": 127, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782357706}, {"pid": 872876331, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 360, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 13:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872875471,45974302,8119]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=5350242]a271628447[/uid] (2026-06-25 13:00):[/b]<br/><br/>半导体今天全部清了，虽然个股都没有放量见顶，但是不吃最后一根红K，感谢狼大。[/quote]<br/>怎么会有这样的理解<br/>我实在虚脱了<br/>我已经把说话水平降低到九年义务教育水平了 ，再往下我不会了啊 我实在不会婴语<br/><br/>不过你们挣钱了总不会挂我上墙 无所谓了。", "lou": 3444, "content_length": 145, "reply_to": 872875471, "14": {"17": 1, "13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782364162}, {"pid": 872879119, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 178, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 13:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872879005,45974302,8128]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60099555]咪了个咕[/uid] (2026-06-25 13:35):[/b]<br/><br/>允许他卖飞[/quote]<br/>外面4000多下跌啊。。。。。。。。。。。。。。这个楼里的人都疯了<br/>我就路过看看 没见过这种场景。", "lou": 3445, "content_length": 95, "reply_to": 872879005, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782365795}, {"pid": 872879395, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 105, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 13:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872878947,45974302,8128]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64587962]身处漩涡之中[/uid] (2026-06-25 13:34):[/b]<br/><br/>我草，石英真比4个2牛逼多了[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>你猜猜谁在里面<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/25/jmQ54-4yxyK8T1kSd3-1i.jpg[/img]", "lou": 3446, "content_length": 56, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/25/jmQ54-4yxyK8T1kSd3-1i.jpg", "size": 9, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/25", "name": "jmQ54-4yxyK8T1kSd3-1i.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 872878947, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782365952}, {"pid": 872880786, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 134, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 13:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872880390,45974302,8132]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67165063]熊猫射手[/uid] (2026-06-25 13:49):[/b]<br/><br/>我说大盘要跳水了，有感觉吗[/quote]<br/>你问他们  他们还在那感叹吃的板少了<br/>叹为观止<br/>感觉他们已经是认为随地捡钱的地步了。", "lou": 3447, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 872880390, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782366767}, {"pid": 872882235, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 94, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-25 14:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872881881,45974302,8136]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=191493]vxxxxv[/uid] (2026-06-25 14:03):[/b]<br/><br/>感觉主力现在还在培养散户形成习惯的阶段？每次下跌都会拉回来？是这样吗[/quote]<br/>。。。。你这不是在重复我之前说过的话么", "lou": 3448, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 872881881, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782367580}, {"pid": 872951107, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 193, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 07:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872950111,45974302,8185]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=331181]xhox[/uid] (2026-06-26 06:53):[/b]<br/><br/>如果最后，金融+半导体+光+新能源同时上去，2天就干到位置<br/><br/>那金融也可以走成像新能源一样的光导之外的主线吗？或者至少一波行情，成为光导在压指数时，反向托指数的一条线？<br/><br/>今天看到一篇文章，和你之前说过的“兜底券商的资金是做科技的机构，你没想到吧”，&quot;基本确认昨天的券商资金是科技那边的了&quot;，类似<br/><br/>[/quote]<br/>你先有个概念就是  这波金融行情，也就是券商+保险+非银的大部分资金是来自科技外溢<br/>为什么这么说呢 <br/>因为先走起来的是长鑫穿透，我之前已经在券商走出来前就说了科技资金会去保底金融，毕竟金融除了银行都不应该继续跌了，否则指数趋势走不上去<br/>毕竟券商+保险新低指数能走出下跌通道？不现实 这是底层逻辑<br/>然后怎么验证呢，你可以看到首先GJD还在减持ETF，但是这几天金融涨停跌停涨停的波动开始加大，那也就是除了正常兜底的被动型社保外有强大的带着盈利思维的短期资金进场，这些钱只能是科技的，因为他们挣钱了 ，下跌通道挣钱了外溢出去，为什么不可能是之前做红利的老登思想的资金的呢，因为他们只会算，这里还差多少更有性价比 ，再跌多少接一点点，他们是没有任何能力以及心气把这些板块做成这个短线样子的。<br/>那总结，既然他是科技外溢，那我的判断他的作用就是关键节点不要拖科技的后退就行，在关键位置做好工具人的属性，比如支撑 压力位的表现需要关注，而不是进去做他，他都是外溢了我为什么要从本来就挣钱的科技跑过去玩他？<br/>这都是跟GJD学的。", "lou": 3449, "content_length": 881, "reply_to": 872950111, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782429958}, {"pid": 872952160, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 124, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 07:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872951752,45974302,8186]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1638060]三少爷的箭[/uid] (2026-06-26 07:41):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，是不是同理可证，做新能源的资金也是科技外溢的资金，而且电池板块的业绩好是公认的，机构也需要做确定性的东西，毕竟亿纬锂能已经打样了，第一个发预告的就是在告诉这些资金我这个板块很靓，快来搞我。<br/><br/>从这些资金来看，最近电池的几个股拿筹码也比较猛，不像准备搞长期做战的准备，一波流到中报就结束了。[/quote]<br/>短期是 长期不是  <br/>电池是有长线资金在里面的 我上半年就已经说过了<br/>所以为什么我做这边，因为他除了短期因为亿纬锂能带来的可能性的新能源中报行情吸引的科技外溢资金 ，还有一批本来就要做下半年电池行情的长线资金<br/>属于双叠加。", "lou": 3450, "content_length": 211, "reply_to": 872951752, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782431494}, {"pid": 872953149, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 97, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 08:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872953063,45974302,8187]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=15359256]&#39;不破楼兰终不还&#39;[/uid] (2026-06-26 08:06):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大  万一后面走下跌 1 而不是 c4 的话  这些长线资金不就被埋了吗[/quote]<br/>对 所以大家都有止损位 你不会有没有吧   ", "lou": 3451, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 872953063, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782432432}, {"pid": 872994883, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 622, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "觉得亏的割肉不就行了 <br/>你们以为我不知道你们？<br/>半导体涨的时候拿3层仓跟，没多少盈利<br/>看见我白纸黑字写的盈利切换新能源  然后自己全仓加杠杆梭哈进去<br/>一个波动都扛不住<br/>在这里嚎叫有什么用，我能打钱给多少个人？<br/><br/>还有 我为什么要打钱给你们？", "lou": 3452, "content_length": 217, "14": {"13": 3, "17": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782450808}, {"pid": 872995141, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 301, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "有低点有机会我也不会再和你们说了 没意义", "lou": 3453, "content_length": 38, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782450949}, {"pid": 872995963, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 305, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在全市场就是把人赶进半导体国产替代<br/>不服你为什么不进？是因为不爱挣钱吗<br/>不就是觉得高了 怕死  但是又反动 就像看个大概低一点的就全部身家梭哈进去 一把翻身<br/>凭什么翻身？<br/>凭你看了几天这个帖子？<br/>你有什么能力让我给你翻身？<br/><br/>一点不付出就白嫖让自己翻身的机会？<br/><br/>我X  XXXX XXXXXX XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX XXXX XXX XXXXXX XXXX", "lou": 3454, "content_length": 283, "14": {"13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782451326}, {"pid": 872997916, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 124, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872997502,45974302,8275]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67153716]名字长了才有人欣赏你[/uid] (2026-06-26 13:34):[/b]<br/><br/>设备不是3.5%吗？？？？？[/quote]<br/>总算有个带眼睛的了", "lou": 3455, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 872997502, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782452247}, {"pid": 872998507, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 187, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:41", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872998073,45974302,8277]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=11609837]3621gg[/uid] (2026-06-26 13:38):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]狼大，早上那个情况是不是跟周二一样？量化受韩国那边影响哐哐砸？[/quote]<br/>全世界都在跌 因为早上那openAI上市延迟的消息<br/>这些人就看个大A分时  还只是上证分时 <br/>我都不懂在看什么<br/>这种炒股最后就是来当肥料的<br/>最后骂人的估计会更难听。<br/><br/>我感觉我救不了几个。", "lou": 3456, "content_length": 166, "reply_to": 872998073, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782452504}, {"pid": 873000377, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 135, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873000025,45974302,8286]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60239810]炒面加蛋[/uid] (2026-06-26 13:52):[/b]<br/><br/>openai推迟上市按说不是好事吗，要是都上市了噶完韭菜后面不就废了。今天下跌是因为这个吗[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>开支方延期上市 -回本周期加长- 投资人预期降低- AI开支降低", "lou": 3457, "content_length": 58, "reply_to": 873000025, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782453341}, {"pid": 873000667, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 298, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 13:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我<br/>在这里输出经验<br/>不代表我是嘴盘<br/>我TMD是真的在这个市场花钱的", "lou": 3458, "content_length": 57, "14": {"13": 1, "14": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782453479}, {"pid": 873001200, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 159, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-26 14:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873000850,45974302,8289]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=40708176]冰室老板[/uid] (2026-06-26 13:59):[/b]<br/><br/>中午看到很多人看到图哥发帖然后跑在这里复读跟